title: Maximize Your Money During These Transitional Times, with Financial Expert Jean Chatzky
description:
Financial expert Jean Chatzky talks real estate, good financial habits to adopt during the pandemic, the safest places to put your money during these unsure times, and how to take risks as safely as possible for the biggest financial upside!

Guest Links:

Don’t forget to check out Jean’s podcast, HerMoney With Jean Chatzky

Websites: https://hermoney.com
